name: Mineral Grandwarf
description: Mineral Grandwarf is an undefeated magical warrior who can travel through dimensions. Guyummy Grandwarf sensed danger approching, so he summoned him. When he arrived in the Shire, he was smaller than ever. The ritual forever turned him into a Grandwarf. It was a most refined summoning choice as Mineral Grandwarf is the very best warrior against inflation. Even his beard is made of gold.
